@NODE Requirements " Requirements "

@{b}@{u}SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS@{uu}@{ub}
Onda requires:

Amiga OS 3.0 or better
Processor 020..060
GfxCon & WirlGIF installed into the same directory.

GfxCon is Cardware / EMailware.
GfxCon is CopyRight © 1997 by Dirk Farin.

WhirlGIF:
 Original version is Copyright © 1995,1996 by Kevin Kadow (kadokev@msg.net).
 Amiga version by Lars Eilebrecht (sfx@unix-ag.uni-siegen.de)

