        @{"      Author       " LINK Author}
@ENDNODE





@NODE Usage "Usage"

@{b}@{u}USAGE@{uu}@{ub}

The mechanism is very simple:
   chose a font (not proportional 8 points),
   insert a string on the field,
   press Start or Test.
The animation is created on Ram Disk.







